<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Refund Policy - D'amour Muslim | Money Back Guarantee</title>
  <meta name="description" content="D'amour Muslim refund policy. 100% money back guarantee within 15 days. Transparent refund process for our Muslim matrimony membership plans.">
  <meta name="keywords" content="D'amour Muslim refund, matrimony refund policy, Muslim marriage service refund, money back guarantee, membership cancellation">
  
  <!-- Open Graph / Social Media -->
  <meta property="og:title" content="Refund Policy - D'amour Muslim">
  <meta property="og:description" content="100% money back guarantee within 15 days. Learn about our transparent refund policy for membership plans.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://damourmuslim.com/refund-policy">

  <!-- Tailwind CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/output.css">
  <!-- Remix Icons -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/remixicon@3.5.0/fonts/remixicon.css" rel="stylesheet">

  <!-- Custom CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">

  <style>
    .guarantee-badge {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a7c59 0%, #2d5a3a 100%);
    }
    .timeline-item::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 2px;
      background: #e5e7eb;
    }
    .timeline-item::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: -4px;
      top: 6px;
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #4a7c59;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-50 font-['Roboto']">
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <main class="pt-24 pb-16 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <!-- Header Section -->
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 font-['Playfair_Display']">Refund Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">100% Money Back Guarantee</p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="ri-calendar-line"></i>
            Effective Date: June 2, 2025
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="ri-refresh-line"></i>
            Last Updated: June 2, 2025
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Money Back Guarantee Badge -->
      <div class="guarantee-badge rounded-2xl p-8 text-center text-white mb-8 shadow-lg">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-20 h-20 bg-white/20 rounded-full mb-4">
          <i class="ri-shield-check-fill text-4xl"></i>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">100% Money Back Guarantee</h2>
        <p class="text-white/90 text-lg">If you're not satisfied within the first 15 days, we'll refund your payment in full—no questions asked.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 material-shadow">
        <!-- Introduction -->
        <div class="mb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            At D'amour Muslim, we are committed to providing exceptional service and genuine value to our members. We understand that choosing a matrimonial service is an important decision, which is why we offer a transparent and fair refund policy. Our commitment is simple: real, suitable proposals. If we cannot deliver what we promise, we'll return your payment in full.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 1: Our Commitment -->
        <div class="mb-8 pb-6 border-b border-gray-200">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 font-['Playfair_Display']">
            <i class="ri-heart-line text-[#4a7c59] mr-2"></i>
            Our Commitment to You
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              When you choose any of our paid membership plans (Premium, Premium Plus, or Executive), we commit to delivering the services outlined in that plan. This includes profile sharing, preference matching, and—for our Premium Plus and Executive members—personalised matchmaking support.
            </p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              We take pride in our work and stand behind our service with a straightforward refund policy that protects your investment.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 2: 15-Day Satisfaction Guarantee -->
        <div class="mb-8 pb-6 border-b border-gray-200">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 font-['Playfair_Display']">
            <i class="ri-calendar-check-line text-[#4a7c59] mr-2"></i>
            15-Day Satisfaction Guarantee
          </h2>
          
          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <i class="ri-checkbox-circle-fill text-green-600 text-2xl mr-3 mt-1"></i>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-900 mb-2">Full Refund Within 15 Days</h3>
                <p class="text-green-800">
                  If you are not satisfied with our service for any reason within the first <strong>15 days</strong> of your paid membership, you are entitled to a <strong>100% full refund</strong>. No questions asked, no complicated process.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <p><strong>How it works:</strong></p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-2">
              <li>The 15-day period begins from the date your payment is processed</li>
              <li>Simply email us at <a href="mailto:contact@damourmuslim.com" class="text-[#4a7c59] hover:underline">contact@damourmuslim.com</a> with the subject line "Refund Request"</li>
              <li>Include your registered email address and the name on your profile</li>
              <li>We will process your refund within 5-7 business days</li>
              <li>Refunds are issued to the original payment method</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 3: Service Delivery Guarantee -->
        <div class="mb-8 pb-6 border-b border-gray-200">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 font-['Playfair_Display']">
            <i class="ri-service-line text-[#4a7c59] mr-2"></i>
            Service Delivery Guarantee (After 15 Days)
          </h2>
          
          <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <i class="ri-information-line text-blue-600 text-2xl mr-3 mt-1"></i>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">Refund for Non-Delivery of Committed Services</h3>
                <p class="text-blue-800">
                  After the initial 15-day period, refunds are available <strong>only if we fail to deliver the services</strong> that were committed as part of your membership plan.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
            <p><strong>What constitutes non-delivery of services:</strong></p>
            
            <div class="grid gap-4 mt-4">
              <!-- Premium Plan -->
              <div class="border rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 flex items-center">
                  <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-[#4a7c59] rounded-full mr-2"></span>
                  Premium Plan (£50 one-time)
                </h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">Refund eligible if:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-1 text-sm">
                  <li>Your profile was not shared across our platforms including WhatsApp groups as promised</li>
                  <li>You did not receive verified, preference-matched profiles</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <!-- Premium Plus Plan -->
              <div class="border rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 flex items-center">
                  <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-[#d4a373] rounded-full mr-2"></span>
                  Premium Plus Plan (£100 + £200 on match)
                </h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">Refund eligible if:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-1 text-sm">
                  <li>All Premium benefits were not delivered</li>
                  <li>You did not receive 1-2 carefully selected profiles per week based on your preferences</li>
                  <li>We failed to provide regular updates and close contact as promised</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <!-- Executive Plan -->
              <div class="border rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 flex items-center">
                  <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-[#8b7355] rounded-full mr-2"></span>
                  Executive Plan (£150 + £450 on match)
                </h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">Refund eligible if:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-1 text-sm">
                  <li>All Premium Plus benefits were not delivered</li>
                  <li>We failed to manage communication with potential matches on your behalf</li>
                  <li>Our team did not provide information promptly and discreetly as committed</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 4: How to Request a Refund -->
        <div class="mb-8 pb-6 border-b border-gray-200">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 font-['Playfair_Display']">
            <i class="ri-mail-send-line text-[#4a7c59] mr-2"></i>
            How to Request a Refund
          </h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="relative pl-8 timeline-item">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Step 1: Send an Email</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Email us at <a href="mailto:contact@damourmuslim.com" class="text-[#4a7c59] hover:underline">contact@damourmuslim.com</a> with subject "Refund Request"</p>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-8 timeline-item">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Step 2: Provide Details</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Include your registered email, profile name, membership plan, and reason for refund</p>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-8 timeline-item">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Step 3: Review</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Our team will review your request within 2 business days</p>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-8 timeline-item">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Step 4: Confirmation</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">You'll receive confirmation of your approved refund via email</p>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-8 timeline-item">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Step 5: Payment</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Refunds are processed within 5-7 business days to your original payment method</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 5: Non-Refundable Situations -->
        <div class="mb-8 pb-6 border-b border-gray-200">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 font-['Playfair_Display']">
            <i class="ri-close-circle-line text-[#4a7c59] mr-2"></i>
            Non-Refundable Situations
          </h2>
          
          <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-4">
            <p class="text-amber-800 text-sm">
              <i class="ri-information-line mr-1"></i>
              Please note the following situations where refunds are <strong>not</strong> applicable:
            </p>
          </div>

          <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>After 15 days, if all committed services have been delivered as described in your plan</li>
            <li>If you have found a match through our platform (for plans with "on match" fees, the match fee is non-refundable once a match is confirmed)</li>
            <li>If your account was suspended or terminated due to violation of our Terms and Conditions or Code of Conduct</li>
            <li>If you provided false or misleading information in your profile</li>
            <li>Change of mind after participating in our matchmaking process beyond the 15-day period</li>
            <li>Services from the Standard (Free) plan—as no payment is involved</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 6: Match Success Fee -->
        <div class="mb-8 pb-6 border-b border-gray-200">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 font-['Playfair_Display']">
            <i class="ri-hand-coin-line text-[#4a7c59] mr-2"></i>
            Match Success Fee Policy
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              For our Premium Plus (£200 on match) and Executive (£450 on match) plans, the match success fee is payable when both parties have expressed mutual interest and agreed to proceed with the proposal.
            </p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              <strong>The match success fee is non-refundable</strong> once:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Both parties have confirmed their interest</li>
              <li>Contact details have been exchanged</li>
              <li>The families have begun direct communication</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
              <i class="ri-information-line mr-1"></i>
              If the match does not proceed after initial contact for reasons outside our control, the success fee remains non-refundable as our service has been delivered.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 7: Contact for Refunds -->
        <div class="mb-6">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 font-['Playfair_Display']">
            <i class="ri-customer-service-2-line text-[#4a7c59] mr-2"></i>
            Contact for Refunds
          </h2>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              For all refund requests and queries, please contact our support team:
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <i class="ri-mail-line text-[#4a7c59] text-xl mr-3"></i>
                <a href="mailto:contact@damourmuslim.com" class="text-[#4a7c59] hover:underline font-medium">contact@damourmuslim.com</a>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <i class="ri-file-text-line text-[#4a7c59] text-xl mr-3 mt-0.5"></i>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-gray-700">Subject Line: <span class="font-medium">"Refund Request"</span></p>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Include: Your registered email, profile name, membership plan, and reason</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Final Note -->
        <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <i class="ri-heart-fill text-green-600 text-xl mr-3 mt-0.5"></i>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-900 mb-2">Our Promise</h3>
              <p class="text-green-800">
                We are fully committed to helping you find your ideal match, by the will of Allah. Our transparent refund policy reflects our confidence in the quality of our service and our dedication to your satisfaction. If you ever have concerns, please reach out—we're here to help.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick Links -->
      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Related Pages</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/pricing" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-white rounded-full shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow text-gray-700 hover:text-[#4a7c59]">
            <i class="ri-price-tag-3-line mr-2"></i>
            Pricing Plans
          </a>
          <a href="/terms" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-white rounded-full shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow text-gray-700 hover:text-[#4a7c59]">
            <i class="ri-file-list-line mr-2"></i>
            Terms & Conditions
          </a>
          <a href="/account-faqs" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-white rounded-full shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow text-gray-700 hover:text-[#4a7c59]">
            <i class="ri-question-line mr-2"></i>
            Account FAQs
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>
